# ZOS Plugin Architecture

## Core Plugins

### 1. Service Manager Plugin
**Path**: `zos-server/plugins/service-manager/`
- Register/manage services
- Nginx configuration
- Port allocation
- UI from my-settings-ui

### 2. Systemd Plugin
**Path**: `zos-server/plugins/systemd/`
- List user services
- Start/stop/restart services
- View logs (journalctl)
- Enable/disable services
- Create new service files

**UI**:
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Systemd Services                        │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ ● zos-minimal-server    [Running]       │
│   [Stop] [Restart] [Logs] [Disable]     │
│                                         │
│ ● leech-lattice-24      [Running]       │
│   [Stop] [Restart] [Logs] [Disable]     │
│                                         │
│ ○ prometheus            [Stopped]       │
│   [Start] [Enable] [Remove]             │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [+ New Service]                         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**API**:
- GET `/api/systemd/services` - List all services
- POST `/api/systemd/services/:name/start`
- POST `/api/systemd/services/:name/stop`
- GET `/api/systemd/services/:name/logs`

### 3. Plocate Plugin
**Path**: `zos-server/plugins/plocate/`
- Search filesystem with locate
- Real-time search results
- Filter by type/path
- Open in file manager

**UI**:
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Search: [nginx                      🔍] │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ 📄 /etc/nginx/nginx.conf                │
