├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [Export] [Filter ▼]                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**API**:
- GET `/api/plocate/search?q=nginx`
- GET `/api/plocate/search?q=*.rs&path=/home`

### 4. Pipelite Plugin
**Path**: `zos-server/plugins/pipelite/`
- Visual pipeline builder
- Door game integration
- Workflow execution
- Status monitoring

**UI**:
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Pipelines                               │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ ▶ Build & Deploy                        │
│   ├─ Nix Build      [✓ Success]        │
