+     1: # eRDFa Pad — Headless Browser Tests
+     2: 
+     3: Nix-based headless Chromium tests for the eRDFa Sneakernet Encoder/Decoder pad.
+     4: 
+     5: ## Prerequisites
+     6: 
+     7: - Nix with flakes enabled
+     8: - The erdfa pad deployed at `/var/www/solana.solfunmeme.com/erdfa/`
+     9: 
+    10: ## Quick Start
+    11: 
